Steps to use:
1. Copy the script and paste in the Appscript editor
2. Click on save project and close the appscript window
3. Open the main Google sheet through which the script has been opened before
4. The refresh it and there should be an option called statistical tests

Steps to add/change:
1. Copy the script and paste in the Appscript editor
2. Modify the script 
3. Test the script
4. then click on RUN and save


Steps tp deploy and publish:
1. Get access to google marketplace by setting a project and enabling the google transfer SDK 
2. Once done follow the steps to authourise the google project
3. ONce the prject has been created change the appscript project to the new project created
4. Deplot the changes
5. Test the deployment
6. Publish the deployment
